OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FMore than 1,300 women gave testimony
OL,7,Fto the inquiry, which, according to
OL,8,Fthe report's authors, found "poor care
OL,9,Fis all frequently tolerated as normal,
OL,10,Fand women are treated as an
OL,11,Finconvenience".
OL,13,FOne woman who had a traumatic birth
OL,14,Ftold ITV News how her daughter became
OL,15,Fstuck during childbirth, suffering a
OL,16,Fstroke and was subsequently diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith mild cerebral palsy.
