OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FHoney Attridge said she was left in
OL,7,F"constant pain" while receiving
OL,8,Fmaternity care for the birth of her
OL,9,Fdaughter Sophie.
OL,11,FHospital staff also failed to
OL,12,Fimmediately diagnose Ms Attridge with
OL,13,Fthird degree tears and only identified
OL,14,Fher injuries six months after she gave
OL,15,Fbirth.
OL,17,F"Because I was a first time mum I just
OL,18,Fdidn't know what was normal and what
OL,19,Fwasn't normal," she said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/12
