OL,6,F"I just felt really kind of alone, I
OL,7,Ffelt like I was the only one and I'd
OL,8,Fsee other mums kind of pushing their
OL,9,Fbuggies around and I'd think 'oh how
OL,10,Fcome they're so happy?'.
OL,12,F"What's wrong with me? I thought it
OL,13,Fwas my fault."
OL,15,FMs Attridge's experience was echoed by
OL,16,FDivina Johnson, who told ITV's Good
OL,17,FMorning Britain she feared death after
OL,18,Fa nurse wrongly administered an
OL,19,Fepidural.
