OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FMs Johnson, who had three traumatic
OL,7,Fbirths, said she felt reduced to a
OL,8,F"vessel that had a baby" while
OL,9,Freceiving maternity care, and that she
OL,10,Ffaced racist abuse from a consultant.
OL,12,FA third of the women who gave
OL,13,Ftestimony to the inquiry said they
OL,14,Fexperienced traumatic births, while
OL,15,Fone out of 25 were left with post
OL,16,Ftraumatic stress disorder (PTSD).
