OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FResponding to the findings, the
OL,7,Freport's authors wrote: "In many of
OL,8,Fthese cases, the trauma was caused by
OL,9,Fmistakes and failures made before and
OL,10,Fduring labour.
OL,12,F"Frequently, these errors were covered
OL,13,Fup by hospitals who frustrated
OL,14,Fparents' efforts to find answers.
OL,16,F"There were also many stories of care
OL,17,Fthat lacked compassion, including
OL,18,Fwomen not being listened to when they
OL,19,Ffelt something was wrong, being mocked
OL,20,For shouted at and being denied basic
OL,21,Fneeds such as pain relief."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/12
