OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FCharlotte Devenish had to have an
OL,7,Femergency hysterectomy after she was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with placenta increta - a
OL,9,Frare condition where the placenta
OL,10,Fattaches itself even more deeply into
OL,11,Fthe muscle wall of the uterus.
OL,13,FHer heart rate dropped and she lost 13
OL,14,Flitres of blood. After 8 hours in
OL,15,Fsurgery, she was put in a coma and
OL,16,Fdidn't meet her daughter for two days.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/12
