OL,6,FShe got PTSD afterwards. She found it
OL,7,Fa lonely and frightening time because
OL,8,Fshe didn't get given any help or
OL,9,Fsupport either for her mental health
OL,10,For her hysterectomy.
OL,12,FThe time was also very traumatic for
OL,13,Fher partner, who she said "saw things
OL,14,Fthat day that nobody should have to
OL,15,Fsee." One of the findings of the
OL,16,Freport is that there is no support for
OL,17,Fpartners either.
