OL,3,CPoor maternity care 'tolerated as
OL,4,Cnormal', report finds
OL,6,FMs Clarke, who pushed for the inquiry
OL,7,Fafter revealing in Parliament that she
OL,8,Ffelt she was going to die after giving
OL,9,Fbirth in 2022, told The Times: "We
OL,10,Fhave listened to mums carefully and
OL,11,Fapplaud their bravery in coming
OL,12,Fforward, sometimes with horrific
OL,13,Ftestimony of how the system failed
OL,14,Fthem and the mental, physical and
OL,15,Feconomic cost of that failure.
OL,17,F"The raft of recommendations we make,
OL,18,Fespecially the appointment of a
OL,19,Fmaternity commissioner, are all
OL,20,Fdesigned to end the postcode lottery
OL,21,Fon maternity services."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/12
